FIG. 3 is a flowchart of a method of determining a discharge time point and a discharge period based on a zero-voltage cross signal and a voltage comparator signal and outputting a switch control signal based on a discharge initiation signal acquired from a microcontroller unit (MCU) according to an example embodiment;

